of the integers between 0 and 20 (inclusively) can be generated by cal
culations on the base numbers usings the operators +,-,*,/,^,! .  In e
ach calculation, at least two of the base numbers must be used and no \+
base number can be used more than once." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 
"" }}{EXCHG {PARA 0 "> " 0 "" {MPLTEXT 1 0 0 "" }}}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
